Paul

Change create cycle for member-owned components (#5365)

Components which were owned by the skin-collective correctly reused
their instances but ones which were member assigned did the wrong
thing. Correct this, which also stops over-creation of the
patch selector, effect chooser, and a few more.

This fixes several things including

1. Closes #5365
2. Fixes an accesibility problem where the patch selector changes instance
3. Generaly churns less